    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 14 (Spell Level 7)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 31 | <b>Successes:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 19 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 39</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, XP</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You shed your damaged body like a snake shedding its skin, and emerge unscathed. You are cured of all poisons and diseases, and are healed 10 HP per level. This technique also removes being blinded, dazzled, deafened, exhausted, fatigued, nauseated, paralyzed, sickened and stunned.<br><br>If you are unable to act normally, you can still activate this technique, though doing so requires a Concentration (DC 20) or Chakra Control check (DC 45). The cost of this technique is half of your maximum Chakra Pool.<br><br>XP - 5,000 XP.</p>\n\n\n\n",
